OL,3,CJudge to decide if man who killed four
OL,4,Cpeople will ever be released from jail
OL,6,FA judge is set to consider whether a
OL,7,Fman who killed four members of the
OL,8,Fsame family in Derrylin in 2018 will
OL,9,Fever be released from prison.
OL,11,F33 year old Daniel Allen had already
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to murdering 19 year
OL,13,Fold Sabrina Gossett, 16 year old Roman
OL,14,FGossett and 15 month old Morgana Quinn
OL,15,Fin Feb 2018 and the manslaughter of
OL,16,Fhis partner 45 year old Denise Gossett
OL,17,Fby way of a suicide pact.
