OL,6,FThe court heard that Allen was found
OL,7,Fstanding bare foot at the porch of the
OL,8,Fburning cottage 'roaring and shouting
OL,9,Fdon't go in there ... I'm sorry. Gone.
OL,10,FGone Gone."
OL,12,FThe court also heard how Allen told a
OL,13,Fparamedic at the scene that, "I'm
OL,14,Fsorry I started the fire."
OL,16,F"A promise is a promise. I promised to
OL,17,Fput them into the next life because
OL,18,Fthey didn't want to stay here no
OL,19,Fmore," he told the paramedic.
