OL,4,Cpeople will ever be released from jail
OL,6,FHe later told a psychiatrist his
OL,7,Fintention was to burn the house down
OL,8,Fand how he expected to die.
OL,10,F"I know they are gone completely
OL,11,Fbecause I killed them. They made me
OL,12,Fpromise."
OL,14,FAllen, who has an address of
OL,15,FMaghaberry Prison, had been living
OL,16,Fwith the family in the Doon Road
OL,17,Fproperty at the time of the fire.
OL,19,FThe Judge was told Allen gave multiple
OL,20,Fconflicting accounts of what happened.
