OL,6,FThe court heard how 15 month old
OL,7,FMorgana's remains were found attached
OL,8,Fto the remains of her mother, 19 year
OL,9,Fold Sabrina - both of them were badly
OL,10,Fburnt on a bed.
OL,12,F16 year old Roman Gossett's body was
OL,13,Fdiscovered in another bedroom and his
OL,14,Fmother, 45 year old Denise was found
OL,15,Fface down with handcuffs attached to
OL,16,Fher.
OL,18,FIt was also revealed in court that
OL,19,FSabrina, Roman and Morganna were dead
OL,20,Fbefore Allen started the blaze but
OL,21,FDenise Gossett was still alive.
