OL,6,FRoman and Morgana died by drug
OL,7,Fpoisoning.
OL,9,FIt is not known how Sabrina died.
OL,10,FAllen claims he strangled the teenager
OL,11,Fbut the prosecution do not accept that
OL,12,Fbecause the 19 year old's blood was
OL,13,Ffound on the defendant.
OL,15,FDenise's cause of death was smoke
OL,16,Finhalation.
OL,18,FSamantha Gossett, Denise's daughter,
OL,19,Fwatched on a video link from England
OL,20,Fand listened to the harrowing details.
