OL,6,FIn her victim impact statement she
OL,7,Fdescribed how the murders have
OL,8,F"shattered her world" and that she
OL,9,Ffound out what happened through the
OL,10,Fpress.
OL,12,FIn her statement, she described the
OL,13,Fongoing daily pain she experiences at
OL,14,Fthis 'devastating loss' and said she
OL,15,Fwill never stop grieving.
