OL,6,FAllen's defence told the judge how his
OL,7,Fclient had a chaotic existence that
OL,8,Fled to this utter catastrophe for
OL,9,Feveryone, saying that his client was
OL,10,Fdysfunctional, disillusional and
OL,11,Fliving in a fantasy world.
OL,13,FAllen originally from England met
OL,14,FDenise Gossett online - Denise was
OL,15,Fliving in Scotland at the time.
OL,17,FThey all moved to the Republic of
OL,18,FIreland from the Doncaster area of
OL,19,FSouth Yorkshire, before renting the
OL,20,Fhouse in Derrylin and had been living
OL,21,Fthere for 14 months before the blaze.
